{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2036","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"大埔轉運站進度報告","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2036-1.jpeg","sequence":2036,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/SbWBKV2LcbvpKt5s/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-09-04T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"大埔轉運站進度報告"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大埔轉運站進度報告"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/ypNLFY2GJjHAfgCP/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FB 李宗豪 2024/09/04"}]},{"type":"text","value":":"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5 月份質詢後，宗豪持續追蹤「大埔轉運站」進度，今日邀請環保局長過來報告，並請周邊鄰近里長一起來聆聽。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n環保局報告："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1、本週焚化爐將整改完成，現行垃圾轉運量約 140 公噸，將逐步下降至每日 80 公噸。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2、將另覓新址，改為室內倉儲密閉作業，配備空污防治設備、污水收集處理設施，倉儲工期約 4 個月，預計今年 11 月發包動工，明年 3 月完工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3、遷址後僅夜間第一趟收運垃圾進入轉運站，減少垃圾停留時間，當日轉運完成。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的立場，遷址及設備優化應是轉運站退場前的短期改善計畫，不應是最終結果，鄉親訴求是轉運站要退場，請市府重視民意！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n我要求："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 垃圾資訊公開透明"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n環保局應上網公告每日進出垃圾量，讓民眾知道垃圾減量效果，並落實當日轉運。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 提供退場要件及期程"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n請環保局提出計畫，需要增加多少垃圾車量？需要增加多少清潔隊員人力？讓垃圾一趟收運不轉運，達到轉運站退場目標。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n還有環境髒亂問題、空污問題，這些都與環保局習習相關，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 我要求成立華亞科空污稽查小組，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 要求增補龜山清潔隊員人力，並再次向局長提出訴求，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 垃圾轉運站目標是要退場，請環保局認真面對！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2036-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2036-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"大埔轉運站進度報告","depth":2,"text":"大埔轉運站進度報告"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2036.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2036.md","_extension":"md"}